entries.s_53: Why hello there! Is there something that I can do for you?
entries.s_55: You can tell me about that pilot you saw.
entries.s_57: Ah, I know who you are now.  I'm glad you came to see me.  I was beginning to wonder if you would.  Listen carefully, head directly northeast.  It's north of some ruins and west of a statue head. Here are coordinates if you prefer that.
entries.s_59: I just wanted to say 'hello' to a lovely lady.
entries.s_61: You are very sweet, but I'm waiting for someone.
entries.s_63: Nothing.  I thought you were someone else.
entries.s_65: All right.  We all make mistakes.
